{
  "stem": "3855.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And speaking Czech, it took no time for me to learn Polish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was already in engineering school there then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But there was a huge, the largest sawmill on the European continent there, owned by a-- actually a Viennese family, but run by a Hungarian family.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They had changed their name from [INAUDIBLE] to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was typical for Hungarian Jews to integrate and change their names.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That was a typical thing to pass.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so I was able to work there for six weeks each summer and spent the remaining six weeks with my uncle, traveling with him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He had a car and a chauffeur.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Even though when it rains there, we had to use what is called droshky, which is a horse-drawn carriage.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because the mud is this high.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "No car can possibly negotiate that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I don't know how it is there today, but I have my suspicions in those little towns.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And so I went with him to these various patients and administering his official duties as the district physician.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And actually, I enjoyed being with him, because he was a very gentle, wonderful fellow, but it didn't take me away from engineering.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And there, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the little towns are mostly Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the farmers around it are, of course, Christians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the joke went that in [INAUDIBLE], there are 50% heathen and 50% [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Yiddinen ?] That's what really means, 50% Jewish and 50% Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Anyway, the Jews had all little stores.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There were-- there was the intelligentsia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There was the lawyer and the doctor and the pharmacist.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they would walk down Main Street every afternoon, and people would greet them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But the little storekeepers put their wares out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And the farmers would all come in on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
